OK, here's the information about the soy nut butter. I can't vouch for this
place as far as ordering (the shipping seems high), but at least you can
see what's in it.

http://www.nutbuster.com/soynutbutter.html

What about making your own? I found this while searching:

http://www.extension.uiuc.edu/archives/experts/health/1998a/0754.html

There are probably other recipes you can find too.

Olivia
